Ping on UART LoRa Modules
=========================

Initiator:
The device that transmits ping frames and waits for reply.

Reflector:
The device that responds to ping frames, then sends reply.

Frame Format:	(Name / Size)
	Start Mark:		1 Byte
	Op-code:		1 Byte
	Frame Serial Number:	4 Byte
	Simple Checksum:	2 Byte

Special Values:
	Start Mark:	0xAA
	OP:		0x80:	Ping
			0xC0:	ACK

Checksum Algorithm:
	CRC16-CCITT

Hardware Wiring:
	Uses defined UART for LoRa module accessing
